text: "Over" is a song and recorded by American country music singer Blake Shelton. It was released in May 2012. ==Music video== The music video premiered on CMT on June 15, 2012. The video debuted at number 20 on CMT's Top 20 Countdown for the week of June 22, 2012. On August 31, 2012, the music video for "Over" took the top spot of CMT's Top 20 Countdown, where it remained for two weeks. ==References== Category:2011 songs Category:2010s ballads Category:Country ballads Category:Country songs Category:Blake Shelton songs
